WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:02.966
Ah, my teeth are inconvenient for you to do.

2
00:00:02.966 --> 00:00:05.366
But what about me?

3
00:00:06.700 --> 00:00:08.200
Wushuang, stop fighting

4
00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:09.333
Go away.

5
00:00:09.333 --> 00:00:11.900
After ten years, I can see you

6
00:00:11.900 --> 00:00:13.166
Die without regrets

7
00:00:13.166 --> 00:00:15.333
Our Lu family can't live without a queen

8
00:00:15.333 --> 00:00:18.400
Dad will help you bear the cost of your treason

9
00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:19.966
Get out of here

10
00:00:20.966 --> 00:00:22.066
Don't you believe me?

11
00:00:22.066 --> 00:00:24.333
You think I'm afraid of thieves and stupid children

12
00:00:24.333 --> 00:00:25.933
The world doesn't believe you

13
00:00:25.933 --> 00:00:27.200
Dad believes in you too

14
00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:30.400
But that's why you have to live well

15
00:00:30.700 --> 00:00:32.233
You take your mother and go

16
00:00:32.366 --> 00:00:33.900
You are my son

17
00:00:33.933 --> 00:00:35.300
Even guilty

18
00:00:35.300 --> 00:00:38.266
Dad will bear all the punishment for you, too?

19
00:00:38.400 --> 00:00:40.033
I'm not leaving, I'm not afraid of you

20
00:00:40.066 --> 00:00:41.966
Go find the best doctor in the world tonight

21
00:00:41.966 --> 00:00:43.066
Heal my mom

22
00:00:43.266 --> 00:00:45.700
It's you, why is the child disobedient?

23
00:00:45.700 --> 00:00:47.733
If you don't leave, it will be too late.

24
00:00:47.733 --> 00:00:49.966
I want to go, I want to be beautiful

